{
  "text": "By using gene ontology resources, such as the PANTHER database, and conventional searches of the literature we were able to assign many of the identified proteins to three major \"functional groups\" which are indicated in Additional File 3, along with supporting references [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
